ygData.messageBody:
Hello Everyone,

I just started a ShadowKnight... level 4 now, but I can't find many quests
for him.

I already talked to everyone in my guild house and the NPC's in the warrior
guild, but I didn't find much. I found the quests to collect beetle eyes..
what a waste 1cp for 2gp worth of eyes. I also found a quest to kill a
paladin. My faction was not high enough in the warrior guild to get the
quests there.

Any advice? What NPC's should I talk to? Are there some quests in another
section of town?

Please share your knowledge my dark brothers.

Zaer
Veeshan
